Three heart-shaped flowers, each with a distinct color scheme and design. The first heart is adorned with a rainbow pattern symbolizing the LGBTQ+ pride, the second heart is yellow with a brown design, and the third heart is orange with red and blue details. The flowers have simple black stems and leaves, set against a plain gray background.

column4: Love has no color and no gender
column7: A chameleon and a heart-shaped figure, both adorned with a rainbow pattern symbolizing LGBTQ+ pride. The chameleon is perched on top of the heart, which has a white area with a simplistic face design on the right side. The primary colors in the mural are rainbow (red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, violet) and white. The background is plain white.

Two silhouetted figures hanging from ropes. Each figure is holding a heart. The figure on the left holds a white heart with a red ribbon tied around it. The figure on the right holds a heart with a rainbow pattern symbolizing LGBTQ+ pride and a white face with simple features. The background of the mural is a solid blue, which makes the black silhouettes and colorful hearts stand out.

A person wearing a black suit with accents of light blue and pink. The person has a purple head with an orange and white heart symbol on the side, and is wearing glasses. The figure's hands indicates a physical disability. The person also wears a swim cap, suggesting involvement in a water sport. The background is a textured black with hints of purple.

Two hands against a rainbow background symbolizing LGBTQ+ pride. The hand on the left is reaching out, adorned with hearts of various colors. The hand on the right is extending a baton towards the other hand. The mural is signed "HEARTCRAFT" on the bottom right.

A person with a beard and curly hair, leaning on a crutch with their right arm. They wears a green shirt with a pink heart on the chest and pink shorts. their left hand is behind their head, giving a relaxed and confident stance. The background is a neutral beige.

A young person in a flowing pink dress, reaching out with their right hand to hold a heart-shaped balloon, surrounded by smaller pink hearts. To the left, the mural includes a quote by Amanda Gorman: "There is always light if you are brave enough to see it. There is always light if you are brave enough to be it." The background is blue; contrasting with the pink elements and the white text of the quote.

A person in a swimming pose with just one arm, possibly depicting a physical disability. The figure is painted in pink against a blue background with white lines resembling swimming lanes. The figure reaches out towards a heart-shaped object that is half white and half orange.

A person in a dynamic pose in a wheelchair. The person is shown in a black silhouette, raising one arm while holding a heart-shaped object that is half white and half orange. The figure is positioned against a neutral-colored wall.

A bouquet of flowers with petals shaped like hearts, each featuring different colors and patterns. The vase holding the bouquet is painted in black and white stripes with a blue and pink ribbon tied around it. The heart-shaped petals include solid colors as well as a rainbow pattern. Colors: wide range of colors, including black, white, red, orange, yellow, green, blue, and the rainbow pattern.

The facade of a two-story building, incorporating the building's architectural features. The upper part has shades of blue, pink, and orange blending into each other. The lower part shows a person, dressed in traditional clothing, weaving or handling loaves of bread against a backdrop of wheat fields. Colors: Blues, pinks, and oranges for the sky, transitioning to yellows, golds, and browns for the wheat fields and the woman’s clothing.

A farmer, standing with hands on hips, gazing over a field of corn and rows of crops. The figure wears a large hat and is silhouetted against a pastel-colored background, with shades of pink, blue, and yellow suggesting either dawn or dusk. The mural uses the building's architectural features, such as windows and lines.

A central figure of a pregnant person sitting cross-legged, their hands gently resting on their belly. To their left is a large sunflower, and to their right is a profile view of another person looking at them. The background includes soft, abstract shapes and natural elements, primarily in shades of pink, purple, and earthy tones.
Four hands coming together in an interconnected manner. The hands are painted in shades of pink and brown, representing different skin tones. The background is a muted mix of green and beige tones.

Three people in an embrace, with the central figure being supported by the other two. The people are dressed in different colors. The people on the left and right are in brownish outfits with a patch or icon on their sleeve, whereas the middle person is in dark clothing with a pink heart symbol. The background is a solid purple.

A fishing village, focusing on the daily life of fishermen and people. Two people are carrying baskets of fish on their heads, while a person is seen working by the water, likely involved in fishing or preparing the catch. The background showcases boats, water, and an abstract, colorful sky with patterns that resemble fish scales. The mural uses warm tones for the background, with orange and brown dominating. The water and boats are depicted in cooler tones of blue and green. The people and the person are in traditional attire, with earthy colors.

A red fox set against a green background. The fox is adorned with intricate patterns and bright colors. On its back, a bird. Grass and plants in the foreground. (Note: "Vulpes vulpes" is the scientific name for the fox, one of the inhabitants of the Serra da Arrábida).
column8:
A similar image can also be found in their website
https://goncalomar.com/project/vulpes-vulpes/

column7: A young person with long dark hair and glasses, seated and holding a potted plant. They are wearing a striped jacket over a black top, blue jeans, and white sneakers. The background is grey, and there are green leaves from a plant depicted above her.
column8:
A similar image can also be found in this link 
https://www.instagram.com/p/CMHw9l5HsIY/

column7: A person wearing a yellow jacket, holding a large potted plant that obscures the head and face. The plant has long, green leaves with stripes, and there are additional plants with large, dark green leaves and red flowers growing from the ground below the figure. The background is a plain grey wall.
column8:
